[I] The Visualization Tool Kit

[T] An open-source, freely available software system for 3D computer
[T] graphics, image processing and visualization. VTK consists of a C++
[T] class library and several interpreted interface layers including
[T] Tcl/Tk, Java, and Python.

[U] https://www.vtk.org/

[A] Kitware, Inc
[M] Roger Mason <rmason@mun.ca>

